Slimcase ft Zlatan – Pongilah The Otumba Lamba himself, Slimcase has started the year in a good fashion as he drops a brand new single entitled “Pongilah.” The record is obviously Slimcase‘s first official single for 2020 and it features Zanku Records head honcho, Zlatan Ibile who gave the jam some lovely spices. SEE ALSO: Slimcase – Lamba Xtra “Pongilah” comes after the release of his previous record tagged “Lamba Xtra.” Beware! the joint is highly infectious, much words not needed anyway. Check it out and share your thoughts below. AUDIO DOWNLOAD ITUNES/APPLE MUSIC The post Slimcase ft. Zlatan – Pongilah appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay